{"tid":1201152,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【尼馬性侵風波】女方哭訴：我正被迫害","createTime":"2019-06-11T02:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T05:35:17.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"373f371ece55e3a059595e337cfc4ef8754d2927","tid":1201152,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:59:12.000Z","msg":"尼馬（Neymar）「強姦案」發生後，當事女主特琳達一直高調在媒體面前揭露事情「真相」。現如今特琳達又一次面對媒體，這一次她沒有爆料「強姦」細節，而是不停的訴苦。<br />\n  特琳達表示：「我不認為現在是繼續談論此事的好時機，我需要恢復一段時間，我現在情況很不好，甚至有了驚恐症，現在我甚至無法好好照料我兒子。」<br />\n  「我現在無法入睡，也吃不下東西，上一週，我廋了10公斤。」<br />\n  「我現在正遭受著很多騷擾，我和我的家人現在都受到了迫害。他們進入我的住處，偷了很多東西，包括我兒子的筆記本電腦。」<br />\n  「人們誹謗我，捏造了很多關於我的事情。」<br />\n  「如果一切可以重來，那我不會在1月份時激活我的IG資料，那時我會停用我的IG，這樣我的生活就一直是平靜的。」<br />\n  特琳達表示，她很後悔使用了IG，因為這正是尼馬和她「勾搭」上的途徑。"},{"pid":"a57a648411b8ef507851a4b188d72d7dd529c8f9","tid":1201152,"uid":128160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639fe660f7ac88ae6ab7e3d80093d71e9792ea3f","tid":1201152,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4af1719567841a3970cb0d5b243cf6120e7e4f","tid":1201152,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc5dff6caa10b571a90a2b934cfe34770f8c5da","tid":1201152,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:08:08.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"2c256be36a973e31f0daa022e60d08ffb98950b8","tid":1201152,"uid":25391,"like":0,"